column1: #Text=This editorial is a perfect example of how out of touch the lamestream media is and why Trump won in the first place.
#Text=It's full of lies and misconceptions that are based on political ideology, one of the biggest being that TPTA is dead.
#Text=The lamestream media is still the lamestream media.
#Text=Did they learn nothing from what they call 'this stunning upset'
